00:27:23.760 --> 00:27:26.220
You have to be the salt and the light of this Earth through Jesus Christ dwelling on the inside of you.

00:27:26.220 --> 00:28:07.695
We are right at the door of the coming of the Lord, and I hope you are being watchful of the times we are living in and being excited, having joy in your heart because the Lord Jesus Christ is about to come back and get us.

00:28:11.004 --> 00:28:13.477
I don't want to be heavy all the time, but a lot of you are clueless.

00:28:13.477 --> 00:28:27.609
You think you can live in sin and make it in the Rapture; you are in trouble.

00:28:36.500 --> 00:28:37.822
I am trying to help you, but you can get mad at me if you want.

00:28:41.379 --> 00:28:42.747
I am trying to tell you the truth because they are not telling you the truth.

00:28:44.670 --> 00:28:46.320
You have to live a lifestyle of holiness.

00:28:46.320 --> 00:28:57.980
If you are living with your boyfriend right now, you are in trouble; you are living in sin and will not make the Rapture.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
You either need to get married or you need to move out.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
You cannot live with your boyfriend in sin; that is called fornication.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.600
You need to give your heart to Jesus Christ all the way and be sold out.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
You cannot live in a compromising situation.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
If you have an addiction to pornography, you have to take steps to change.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
Put blocks on your computer and phone, have an accountability partner, and start steering your ship right.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
You cannot keep going down the wrong path and saying, 'Well, God's grace covers this.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.050
' There is a season of grace when you are a baby Christian, but as you get older, you have to grow up.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
If you want to walk in the glory and the fire, you have to walk in holiness.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
When you mess up, take communion and ask God to forgive you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
God is a good God.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
I mess up too; I have issues, and I go to Him immediately.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
Run to God when you sin, don't run from Him.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
You don't want to miss the Rapture of the church.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
Jesus Christ is coming, and hell is real.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
If you are living in sin, you are going to hell.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
Turn or burn.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
Get right with the Lord, read your Bible, and follow it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Love speaks the truth.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.100
Everyone is always trying to sugarcoat it because they don't want to offend people, but Jesus told us that in the end, many will be offended.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.350
People are walking around in offense like crazy right now—at church, on the internet, on Facebook, and on X, not Twitter.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.300
We have to walk in love, speak the truth, and tell people what the Bible says about sin.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
I want to pray for you right now and believe God for your miracle.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.650
Father, whatever they are believing for right now, I speak healing over their bodies in the name of Jesus.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
I speak to cancers, diabetes, heart disease, and AIDS.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.650
I curse the spirit of AIDS in the name of Jesus and command it to go from their bodies.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
I call their blood to be clear.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
To any kind of sexually transmitted disease: we command you to go in the name of Jesus.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
Repent and stop sleeping around.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
Lord Jesus wants to heal your body.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
We call for deliverance from migraine headaches, cataracts, and eye issues.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
Whether the iris is detached, I command you to be healed in Jesus' name.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.600
I call arthritis in the hands to be healed and sciatic nerve pain to be gone.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Father, I thank You.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
I speak to prostate problems right now and curse prostate cancer in Jesus' name.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
I just saw a colon again.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
I call your colon healed in Jesus' name.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Colon cancer, be gone.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
I heard the word 'diverticulitis.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
' Be healed in Jesus' name.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
I decree the colon is whole.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Constipation, go.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
Fibromyalgia and lupus, go in Jesus' name.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
I command healing and wholeness over you.
